Class CompressedTrieLexicon

  • java.lang.Object
    • TrieLexicon
      • CompressedTrieLexicon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ILexicon, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.String>

    public class CompressedTrieLexicon
extends TrieLexicon
    Removes nodes with only one child. A chain of nodes pointed to by one link can be compressed into a node storing a suffix rather than a single character.
